ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString:
Set(varSelectedEmployee, ThisItem);

ClearCollect(
    colDocStatus,
    {Doc:"Duty List OC",   Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.'Duty List OC'.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Duty",           Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.Duty.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Appointment OC", Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.'Appointment OC'.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Appointment",    Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.Appointment.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Character Certificate", Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.'Character Certificate'.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Fitness Certi.", Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.'Fitness Certi.'.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Cheques",        Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.Cheques.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Surety Bond",    Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.'Surety Bond'.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Nomination Form",Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.'Nomination Form'.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Offer Oc",       Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.'Offer Oc'.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Previous Experience", Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.'Previous Experience'.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Education",      Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.Education.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"KYC",            Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.KYC.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Resume",         Status: If(varSelectedEmployee.Resume.Value="YES"," Complete"," Missing")},
    {Doc:"Adhaar No.",     Status: If(IsBlank(varSelectedEmployee.'Adhaar NO.')," Missing"," Complete")},
    {Doc:"Pan Card No.",   Status: If(IsBlank(varSelectedEmployee.'Pan Card NO.')," Missing"," Complete")},
    {Doc:"Address",        Status: If(IsBlank(varSelectedEmployee.Address)," Missing"," Complete")}
);

Set(varCompleted, CountIf(colDocStatus, Status = " Complete"));
Set(varTotal, CountRows(colDocStatus));
Set(varProgress, If(varTotal > 0, Round(varCompleted / varTotal * 100, 0), 0));

Navigate(EMPJOURNEYSCREEN, ScreenTransition.Fade)
